description:
Gen 0 Bloodshed Bears are the first Bloodshed Bears collection. 

Welcome to the Bloodshed Bears NFT game deployed on the Ethereum Blockchain.

The BloodShed Bears game combines P2E, risk, upgradeable meta and regular faction wars into a unique game experience.

Each Bloodshed Bear is randomly assigned one of two factions upon mint and has a 10% chance of being a 'Elite' which can steal $BLD or reinforcement mints from your rival faction.

**Staking has started, true number of unique wallets is ~2500**

Shadow Quest is a *3-in-1* NFT project: **Next-gen P2E game** + **Lore** + **Art**

***Discord https://discord.gg/shadowquest***

~_**① Next-gen P2E game:**_~

✅Enter the ancient lands of Ashtaar and battle your warriors in different locations to earn $HONR coin. In this epic war, battles occur every hour and the amount of $HONR you earn depends on your warrior’s stats – so you’ll have to be strategic!

✅There are 9,996 hand-drawn warriors, of which 999 are from the Dark Samsar nation who have mysterious powers that enable them to challenge warriors to unique fights and steal $HONR.

✅All of this is built from scratch on an optimized ERC-721:SHADOW contract where gas is 1/3 of normal, with innovative off-chain links to reduce gas further for more enjoyable tactical gaming.

~_**② Lore:**_~ Deep lore is intricately woven into the game and art, with over 50% has been submitted by the community.

~_**③ Art:**_~ See below!

description: Neural play is collection of unique NFTs generated by a neural network. Our task was to create a multimodal neural network that studies concepts in several modalities, namely in the verbal and visual forms, in order to build a better understanding of the world. The transformer is taught to autoregressively model text and image tokens as a single data stream. On the Christofari cluster, the model was trained for 37 days on 512 TESLA V100 GPUs, and then another 11 days on 128 GPUs - a total of 20352 GPU days.

Generative Transfer Art Project 1 is the first in a series of experimental projects by [Wilson Cusack](https://twitter.com/WilsonCusack). Each NFT's image is created by its first 16 transfers, populating a 4x4 grid of squares. A new colored square is added on each transfer. The to address of the transfer determines the color.

There are 64 originals. Each original has up to 16 editions/copies, depending on the number of times transferred. Due to a bug, editions/copies mint more editions/copies when they are transferred. Please do due diligence to know whether you are buying an original or a copy. Copies do not add to the NFT art are when transferred, only the originals do. 

If the number at the end of the url matches the displayed "Token #...", then it is an original. There is also a [collection of wrapped originals](https://opensea.io/collection/wgtap1-og). Visit our website and Discord for more info.

description:
HENI is delighted to present The Currency, the first NFT collection by Damien Hirst. Reimagining the way NFTs are used, The Currency is a collection of 10,000 NFTs which correspond to 10,000 unique physical artworks which are stored in a secure vault in the UK. The works are now brought to life through their launch on the blockchain.

Starting with the creation of the physical artworks in 2016, The Currency explores the boundaries of art and currencyâ€”when art changes and becomes a currency, and when currency becomes art. Successful applicants will all initially receive NFTs. Ultimately, you have to decide between the digital NFT or the physical artwork, both of which are artworks in their own right. Whichever you pick, the other gets burned.

The collection is on the Palm blockchain, which is a new token-powered ecosystem for NFTs connected to Ethereum. It is 99% more energy efficient than proof of work systems such as Ethereum or Bitcoin. The Currency NFTs can be moved to Ethereum.

Zerion Genesis Collection, 2021. The Genesis Collection was designed in collaboration with Nikolay Ironov, an AI artist created by the design studio Art. Lebedev.

description:
This project is an experiment about composability in NFTs. The pieces are generated on mint, using instructions from Autoglyphs together with random characteristics. Autoglyphs were chosen because they're the first and most important generative art project, fully contained on-chain, which allows deeper composability. Two pieces generated from the same generator will not be equal.
The artwork consists of lines that are carefully spread across the canvas. This project is an ode to shapes derived from round-ended lines and complexity from chaos. It has inspiration from microscopic nature and movement.

Visit the website: <https://avidlines.art>

CryptoFoxes are the only NFTs minted with a slot machine on the Ethereum blockchain. They are 11,111 for sale on [www.cryptofoxes.io](https://cryptofoxes.io/). They are the second generation of our collection. All the important details about the collection are on [www.cryptofoxes.io](https://cryptofoxes.io/).

All the assets are handcrafted, then the CryptoFoxes are generated with a Python script in 48x48 GIF and scaled to 480x480 and minted on a Smart Contract ERC721 on Ethereum Blockchain. Each one is unique and crafted with its properties. Some of them are super rare!

Follow our [Twitter](https://twitter.com/CryptoFoxesNFT) for the latest news and join our [Discord](https://discord.gg/3crJeNYssT) to chat with the community.

The Origin collection is [here](https://opensea.io/collection/cryptofoxes-origin-steak).

description:
Randomly generated and fully on-chain squiggly lines, the first project in the Atlantes series. Only 100 pieces were created during the minting process.  The on-chain generator has now been shut off forever so they are only available in the secondary market. Project was launched in October 2020.

Curve type refers to the type of bezier curve used in the on chain algorithm. All curve types had an equal probability of being created.
Any auctoineer who called the end auction function for a given auction was credited as the creator of that Squiggly as they generated the seed to create the art for the auction winner and new owner.

created by natealex

description: Neural play is collection of unique NFTs generated by a neural network. Our task was to create a multimodal neural network that studies concepts in several modalities, namely in the verbal and visual forms, in order to build a better understanding of the world. The transformer is taught to autoregressively model text and image tokens as a single data stream. On the Christofari cluster, the model was trained for 37 days on 512 TESLA V100 GPUs, and then another 11 days on 128 GPUs - a total of 20352 GPU days.

The line man NFT

Hello,

I am a young artist. I turned 11. I have been holding a pencil and brushes since I could hold something. And even earlier, when I still could not hold anything in my hands, my mom sat me down on a huge paper on the floor and I drew with my fingers, palms, feet and knees. The huge paper became a real painting in my eyes. It took a long time for my mom to bathe me after.

Since then I have been drawing on paper of different sizes. Even not only on paper, but on stones, wood, walls, clothes, flower pots, cat's tail (oops, don't tell anyone, this is my little secret).

Once I painted a pleasant scent. Relatives were very surprised at my passion for painting smells. It was a time of research.

On my OpenSea page, you can see my paintings on small sheets of paper.

Welcome to my collection. I wish you a pleasant time.

Sincerely, Maria Tropinina

Weird Whales is an NFT collection created by twelve-year-old programmer [Benyamin](https://linktr.ee/ObiWanBenoni) from London, UK who began learning to code at the age of five. The project started as an educational endeavour. Benyamin created all the base and trait layers for the whales (normal, zombie, ape, alien), he then generated 3350 unique digital collectibles programmatically using an open-source Python script.

The project success and backstory forms a core part of early NFT, generative art and digital collectible history. It has been featured in [The New York Times](https://tinyurl.com/4kwsrp4r), [Business Insider](https://tinyurl.com/2yxjv8ae), [CNBC](https://tinyurl.com/3xezwxkd), [The Telegraph](https://tinyurl.com/unpst3fu), The Guardian, ITV News, BBC, NY Post, Decrypt and many more.

Benyamin was invited to [speak](https://youtu.be/XHUWaLcLau8) about NFTs at Pembroke College, Oxford University. He is the youngest person to lecture at the college, founded 1624.

This is a collection of neo-expressionistic cyber paintings by me, Ramon Bruin.
These are created with a drawing pad, digital oil brushes and crayons on Photoshop. I paint these ones exactly like I paint in real; with a lot of motion, feeling, sarcasm and a dash of cynicism. The topics are daily life observations and my ongoing flow of thoughts. 
My goal is to create cool neo-expressionistic paintings for people to collect and to exhibit in their own homes. With the upcoming nft tv's I want people to have bad-ass digital paintings at home.

description:
Every day in January 2022 I generated a new output from an algorithm, generated a random wallet address, and sent the work to that address. On the final day, January 31st, all the previous Dead Ringers were placed in a 5 by 6 grid and minted to a generated address.

It was almost guaranteed none of the wallets that received Dead Ringers would ever be accessible given there are 16 to power of 40 available addresses. I hoped it would help observers appreciate the vastness of the address space and the underlying security it provides to the network used to distribute the work.

The Dead Ringers: Edition flips that notion on its head. Now an edition of January 31, 2022, colloquially known as the Dead Ringers grid, is available for every address if they want one. An edition size capped at 16 to the power of 40.

268 original drawings created on paper, using colored pencil, graphite, ink and watercolor plus 7 works painted in acrylic on wood panels. Now with the digital Lightbody Collection their imagery literally glows. 

The Lightbody is a recurring archetype in the history of Art. Ancient petroglyphs show solarized figures with haloes and rays of light emanating from the body.  Appearing in the earliest icons of Hindu, Buddhist and Christian art are portrayals of haloes, auras, chakras, all manner of glowing life energies that, through paintings and sculpture, make the subtle visionary worlds visible, symbolically merging physical human forms with the light of spirituality.

MEV Army is a collection of shadowy super coders lurking in the Ethereum dark forest, ready to exploit transactions. MEV, as initially defined by Phil Daian in Flash Boys 2.0, stands for Miner Extractable Value. MEV is additional value captured by miners who censor and reorder transactions in blocks they produce.

Each member of the MEV Army is composed of the original transaction ordering code from go-ethereum. Miners are not the only 'players' who can capture MEV; they include transaction searchers, liquidators, sandwichers, backrunners, time-bandits, and generalized frontrunners are scattered throughout the dark forest. These represent some of the traits in the MEV Army Collection.

On November 16, 2021 [xellirk](https://twitter.com/XellirkST) set out on a quest to deliver 365 gm's (one for each day of the year) to the great [Cozomo de' Medici](https://twitter.com/CozomoMedici). 

On January 20, 2022, Cozomo de' Medici acknowledged the quest and raised the stakes in this Twitter post -> https://twitter.com/CozomoMedici/status/1484332055387275268

100% of initial proceeds will be donated to charities (~$21,000 USD). That means that every 91 gm's that are sold, ~$5,250 will be donated to a charity -- Cozomo will choose the first. Collectors will choose the charities for the 3 remaining donations.

The KOKingsNFT project brings you the world's first premier NFT boxing collector cards series. Each boxer card comeS in 4 varieties indicating the level of scarcity and will have unique characteristics:

*UNIQUE CARD - This 1 OF 1 ULTRA RARE card features unique motion graphics and highly desirable designs. 
*CHAMPION CARDS - These SUPER RARE cards will feature unique motion backgrounds and fighter animation
*PROSPECT CARDS - These RARE cards will feature unique motion backgrounds 
*FIGHTER CARDS - These REGULAR cards feature unique fighter designs

Our vision for the project is centred around the concept of collecting rare sports cards in a sport we hold close to our hearts. We also recogniser the unique opportunity that NFT capability can bring. Verified record of ownership & the ability to assign real-world benefits to card holders opens up many doors of possibilities. description: The MotleySpiders is a collection of 108 unique, completely handcrafted spiders NFTs, with proof of ownership stored on the Ethereum blockchain. Every card in this collection is 8-bit color 24x24 pixel art image of real-life spider in PNG format. This is not ordinary collectibles, but a digital puzzle. All spider images from this collection were combined into one 8-bit color 576X576 pixel art image in PNG format. This image was encoded in base64 code, and then original image was completely destroyed. The resulting base64 code was programmatically splited into 108 parts, which was randomly shuffled and distributed between all cards of this collection in unlockable content. Also, all but one card contains in unlockable content a name of card in which you can find the next part of base64 code. Thus, only the person who owns each card, at least once, will be able to collect all parts of the resulting base64 code, and will know the sequence in which these parts need to be assembled.

description:
**MetaNouns** are a never-ending, completely automated art derivative of [Nouns.wtf](https://nouns.wtf/)

---

A MetaNoun is a Noun send to the Metaverse, and thanks to the SVG filetype it is possible to Meta-pixelate the distance from the point of the noun to the metaverse.
This algorithm results in the noun being modified as it has traveled through the metaverse. Hence the name Metanoun.

*This algorithm is a free interpretation of the developer's own metaverse, and has no chosen meaning, it is an artistic approach.*

---

The **MetaNouns contract** talks with the Nouns contract and generates a MetaNoun from this conversation. 
As long as there are Nouns, there will be MetaNouns.

Because Nounders have chosen to compensate themselves with nouns for the first 5 years of the project with every 10th noun (noun ids #0, #10, #20, #30 and so on), the MetaNoun contract creates *every 10th MetaNoun without metaversing the glasses*.

description:
Website: https://ethwalkers.io

ETH Walkers is a Zombie Apocalypse-themed NFT project with a playable social RPG game.

At the start of the game, 60 Zombie Bored Apes will burst onto the scene and begin "biting" the human players. Once bitten, human characters will turn into human zombies, who will then go on and bite additional human players. Over the coming days, the zombie population will grow from the original sixty, to hundreds, and then to thousands, until there are only a few human survivors left.

The goal is to survive and be one of the final 100 humans remaining in the game. Along the way, players will make daily decisions about what part of the town to explore, whether to hunt for resources and weapons or to steal them from other players. There will be factions to join and mysteries to solve. The decisions you make and the company you keep will determine whether your character lives or forever walks the earth as one of the undead...

description:
Galaxy Metaverse is a collection of 10,000 solar system NFTs, 3000x2000px unique digital collectibles living on the Ethereum blockchain. Each solar system is unique and made from randomly combining 344 different elements. All solar systems are beautiful and unique, but only some have rare traits like golden & platinum comets and planets.

We created this collection so that people like ourselves can show their love for space and science. To allow them to collect and become the owners of the unexplored parts of galaxies and solar systems. Science, Space and Sci-Fi lovers have finally got their project! 

Buy our NFTs and become a Star-Lord and join our community!

We Star-Lords love to help the others, 10% of all sold items will go to a charity named Fight for Forgotten dedicated to building wells in Africa.

My work is a dive into my personal relationship with fears and how they can be thought of in different ways in order to make them less of a burden. By using playful figures in cartoon-like stances I am giving my fears a more childlike view and making some harsh realities a little more palatable for any viewers. Each photo explains a different fear from more metaphorical things such as loss in general to more literal subjects like the fear of getting older or dying. The work follows the same character in different forms to represent me, but also to put the viewer into the perspective of the one man shown to relate to some of the more common fears.

description:
Hi everybody,

This NFT collection is created to send messages to other wallets. Because transactions on the blockchain are public and can't be altered, stopped or erased it is possible to check if a certain nft of this collection has been send to a certain wallet adres. That way there is a certain amount of public vision of how an owner of a wallet adress behaves. If they get a lot of negative NFT's, it's likely the owner isn't nice. In this way the NFT collection can be seen as a wallet review collective. It is also a way to communicate to a walletadress which functionality is still lacking. 

I'm a single person operating and i'm not tech savvy. If received positively by the community it might develop further. For ideas or to get in contact, please send me a message on discord. I'm also not an artist. My editing skills are poor although the way the pictures are made may appeal to people because of the 90's feel of it. 

Kind Regards,

Crypto Art Mes is art generated by combining famous art pieces and running a cryptographically generated mesh over them.

GM, 365 is a collection of pieces created each morning on the day they are minted to the blockchain.  When they are posted is based on when I have the ability to log onto Opensea.. A tweet always gets sent as soon as it's minted.

Prince increase after every 10 new holderz

_MintMe is a love letter to our inner selves and a reminder to embrace who we are and celebrate our individuality._

**#BeYourself**



_*Pricing*_:


*#1 to #250 are free.*


*#251 to #2500: 0.01*




*MintMe is in no way related to CryptoPunks or Larva Labs*
